USE CASE NULL OBJECT PATTERN :

Issue :

# Jab bhi hum kisi method sa kuch get karta hai by employee ** but ma emp null bhejta hu to NPE ** ayaga.
# Agar Maina NP ko handle kar liya if(emp != null) but yeah muliple class main hai to mujhe har time if(emp != null)
    same line likhni hogi.

# Isko avoid karna ka liya NULL OBJECT PATTERN Aya.




NULL OBJECT PATTERN POINT WHEN THEY WORK :

* A null object replaces NULL return type.
* No need to put IF CHECK for  Checking NULL.
* Null Objects reflects do nothing or Default behaviour.